                        <interp inst="t18380226-name-1195" type="given" value="AMELIA"></interp>AMELIA HERRING</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a broker's shop. The female prisoner sold me two chairs, on Friday night, the 1st of February—these are them—(<hi rend="italic">producing two chairs.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
