               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183802260206"></xptr>
               <p>Monday last—she was remanded—I went <hi rend="italic">to</hi> the lodgings, and found the property was missing—that was the room they had occupied since that left the prosecutor's—the man was then in custody on another charge—I did not take him.</p>
